<p><a href="https://grounded2.obsidian.net/news/update-0-3">The official blog post announcing the update</a> has also teased the return of both the Masked Stranger and the Snake Colossus, which you'll have to track down with an updated mutation system allowing you to further customise your ability to build or fight in Grounded 2.</p>
<p>The team at Obsidian also stated it's working on Playgrounds mode, a fan-favourite from the original game.</p>
<p>If you've not played Grounded 2, you can read <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/grounded-2-early-access-review">Eurogamer's review of its Early Access release</a>. In it, Robert Purchase wrote: "The ant-sized thrills of Grounded return in a sequel which lays exciting foundations for the future. There's work to do but, already, an exciting adventure to have. "</p>

